    person("Ivan", "Cakic", email = "ivan.cakic.2023@muail.ie", role = c("aut"))
  )
Description: This package will include 1 (or two) inbuilt dataset(s) on
    202* English Premier League Odds (and 202* Wimbledon odds).  These
    datasets will be "bettr" datasets.  This package will also contain a
    function to transform data frames into "bettr" datasets and a generic
    function to plot (and possibly predict()) "bettr" data.
